comment_regular_data.body:
> support the normal case where `nvim` spawns the server as a child. [use detach=true](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/23093#issuecomment-2337867984)?

~~I haven't been able to get the "stdio" client to detach without also bringing down the server.~~

Update: resolved, see https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/30319#discussion_r1757092230


---

